  "body": "If you are using one of these matchers, it would be natural to make this mistake:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nawait expect(tx).to.be.revertedWithCustomError(c, \"Error\", arg1, arg2)\r\n```\r\n\r\ninstead of the correct\r\n\r\n```js\r\nawait expect(tx).to.be.revertedWithCustomError(c, \"Error\").withArgs(arg1, arg2)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe should throw an error in these cases.",
